
What is it?
~~~~~~~~~~~

In this package you'll find the Khepera robot serial communication routines
for MATLAB for the Un*x environment.  In particular, these are kopen, ksend
and kclose.  They were developed as part of a research project to exploit
the Khepera robot on Un*x workstations.  They are aimed to be same (where
appropiate) functionality wise than those for the PC or Mac.

This package is (C) 1999 Matthias Grimrath <m.grimrath@tu-bs.de>. 
Modifications are (C) by their respective owners.

For installation instructions see 'Makefile'.

